fitsio.h  No change

gmrt_newcorr.h No change.

longnam.h No Change

makefile  changes associated with the option of using SLA/NOVAS for the rotation.

novascon.h header file for NOVASC

novas.h    header file for NOVASC

novas_prenut.c NOVAS based functions to do the precession/nutation etc.

nutation.h header file for NOVASC

plot_flagged.py  No change

plot_postcorr.py added replacement of NaN with zeros.

Readme -- this file.

read_rawvis.py No change. This needs to be updated to reflect the fact that the raw visibility files now have the index embeded in them.

solarsystem.h Header file for NOVASC

sla_prenut.c  SLA based functions to do the precession/nutation etc.

sla
stats.c -- No change

SVFITS.md  usage docummentation - updated to reflect changes.

svfits.c -- changes associated with giving the option of using SLA/NOVAS and also integrating the data further in the ALL_DATA mode.

svfits.docx -- a brief report on svfits. updated  to reflect changes

svfits_par.txt -- updated to include the relevant new options.

svio.h -- small changes corresponding to the new options in svfits.

svsubs.c -- added option of using SLA/NOVAS for the coordinate rotations, the SLA version compares very well with images from the 1s LTA file. Various other smaller changes.




